title: 2: Can Barnes & Noble Turn the Page?
description:
In today's episode of Barron's new podcast, The Readback, Alex Eule talks to Barron's Andrew Bary about the book industry and Barnes and Noble's next chapter.

The Readback is hosted by Alex Eule and produced by Mette Lützhøft.
